[assistant] Fixed the failing test and committed the change.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Cause:
[assistant] - Newer `javac` can omit the synthetic `this$0` field for non-static inner classes if the inner class does not actually use the outer instance.
[assistant] - Because `InnerDocument` did not reference `OuterClassMapperTest.this`, `OuterClassMapper` saw no `this$0` field and returned the original member name.
